Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.64,0:00:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.96,0:00:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.17,0:00:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.97,0:00:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.25,0:01:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.69,0:01:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.36,0:01:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.00,0:01:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.74,0:01:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系統]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.28,0:01:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把戰況裡出現的一切資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即時運算後\N得出的龐大預測值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反饋給駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.75,0:01:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛艙系統的俗稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這系統甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把駕駛員趕進極端狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現完美的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果連自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界變得混沌的時代裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.21,0:01:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為最強兵器的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飛翼零式和次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十五話\N[五飛復出]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是特洛瓦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我啊，凱薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱賽…琳…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特…特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是先鋒，現在進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳給我修練的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我十分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣，你能成長到這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙龍鋼彈也會樂意認同你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新完成的哪吒好強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不夠資格駕禦它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量就是心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.88,0:03:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心就是和自己戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不戰勝自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.59,0:03:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就永遠不能打倒你的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們數百年以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直和宇宙的惡魔戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長年累月保護我們的這衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連維持生命的能力也已失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引領我們走上滅亡之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.01,0:04:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要遵從天命\N把正義貫徹到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白嗎?五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是相信自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不欺騙自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出賣自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對步向滅亡的人也不留情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超老師，我一定要戰勝敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的戰鬥對手是惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，你不用猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你並非打倒惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打倒的人，那就是惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義由我來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我們的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.97,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是雙龍鋼彈的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來，05
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是先鋒，逼他出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰進入第二階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了!05
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.29,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒，引領我走上正確之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始攻擊0200衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了，是05
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止無謂的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備了攻擊0200衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你繼續抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就會連累整個衛星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了，五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一族的末裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一族到最後\N也不可忘記尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.43,0:07:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛會繼承我們的遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.55,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛，別猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.99,0:07:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的猶豫會產生進一步的戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥吧  五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了自己的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義由我來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,L5的衛星附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來有大規模的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛或許行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.04,0:08:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是05的駕駛員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的戰力\N是這艘艦和飛翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要正面和羅姆斐拉作戰\N戰力不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.39,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能招攬他為同志嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是困難的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員只有獨自戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.36,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知他會否幫助\N身負大義的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有共同敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.04,0:09:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有機會談一次的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把航路轉向L5方面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新星作戰的功效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經令全世界的大部份國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸入我們羅姆斐拉財團的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.82,0:09:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，新星作戰到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我要你繼續出任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次作戰的指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次作戰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有責任維護和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那須要壓倒性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.64,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N只要有MD就夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD只能在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,局部地區發揮力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對大局帶來更大效果的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我命令你製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬年和平級宇宙戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇…宇宙戰艦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奧的情報是可靠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.81,0:10:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我一直以來認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會麻煩馬格亞那隊的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是不敢前去找他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在不是說那種話的時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉把特列斯派的主力擊潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，全世界的勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣傾向羅姆斐拉方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說山克王國是風中燭火也不為過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是為了從其魔爪裡\N保護這國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去領取沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告，這裡是戰鬥空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快繞道飛去URW地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不遵照指示就把你擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.68,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不誘導就要擊落我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我，我的沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在來找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.01,0:11:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國的確曾經隸屬羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在，羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只從本國搾取軍費
