Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.09,0:12:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是為了滿足自己的支配慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.76,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子和從前的聯合毫無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白各位的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能靠軍事力量得到一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣豈不是清楚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳帶領我們踏上和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有渺小的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果各位渴望得到真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為也有可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.55,0:12:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令羅姆斐拉財團停止軍事活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各國的代表回國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位看來很滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連山克王國一國的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也無法維持的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以承諾其他國家得到和平嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.72,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團承諾的和平\N是虛假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.45,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特的完全和平\N才是實在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.72,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各國的代表也以那主義為依歸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉的軍事力量太強大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在特列斯‧克修里那達失勢後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人作為向心力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理財團代表的迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.51,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能勝任吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的羅姆斐拉不足為懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.32,0:13:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請莉莉娜殿下妳提起精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現妳的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要妳護航，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不是特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你們一樣只是近衛兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是OZ特列斯派的餘黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,習慣很難改掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以叫妳諾茵隊長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你們那樣心安理得，隨便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受紀律束縛的軍事組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一點你們別忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這個國家集結軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉就不會袖手旁觀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何容納那班人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是那件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想知道的話，你就來這邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，在山克王國的周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團的主力正不斷集結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次盧森堡特列斯派殲滅作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.32,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們打算保留當時的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.43,0:15:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進攻山克王國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換言之，羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.93,0:15:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就沒打算放過我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會和從前的山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏上同一命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只有渺小的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對抗羅姆斐拉財團的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好容納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.75,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們這些特列斯派和舊聯合餘黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣解釋能令你同意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好勇敢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這麼龐大的軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天或許就會攻來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.86,0:15:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們擁有\N名為鋼彈的希望象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別抱有太大的期望比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和卡特爾不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得保護這國家沒有意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.11,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你帶來的特列斯大人的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引領很多士兵來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為對抗羅姆斐拉的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這東西交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟打算做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木偶始終只有這點技倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒人堂堂正正和我戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.12,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD部隊\N全軍覆沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法，撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把生死倚靠機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類就會墮落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.77,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒OZ或許要趁現在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.35,0:17:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈05，這裡是萬年和平號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛翼零式?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.36,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和你談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!我不是你的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敵人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為宇宙帶來戰鬥的惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們才要一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ、羅姆斐拉財團戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不是OZ的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.27,0:18:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會相信倒戈相向的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要怎樣做\N你才肯認真聽我講?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試打倒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.62,0:18:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無疑問是鋼彈駕駛員才有的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N不愧是改良了的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不倚靠它就無法取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬年和平號?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些映象究竟是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.26,0:19:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我的敵人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.16,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的戰鬥對手不是這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯!振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被零式系統擺佈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯，他會成為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顯示所有資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後消除戰士猶豫的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那只會產生悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為沒人比被機械擺佈的戰士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更可悲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要現在的傑克斯克服它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許太苛刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!明天就要出發啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,團長\N這個衛星的人也很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.92,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何突然要上演最後一場啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞鋼彈出現在附近的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做…做甚麼?特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這套衣服…放在哪裡才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那套衣服? 不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之後幫你放好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.94,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要聽姐姐的話啊，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一日收容那傢伙在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就不知道\N何時會被牽連吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.39,0:21:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.16,0:21:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢，他失去記憶雖然可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.33,0:21:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但特洛瓦這樣子比較幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.73,0:21:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈…是甚麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.30,0:21:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我覺得好親切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.87,0:21:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好冷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.28,0:22:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.11,0:22:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再讓你上戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會保護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.84,0:22:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.84,0:22:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.84,0:22:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.34,0:22:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.84,0:23:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.34,0:23:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.84,0:23:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙，迪歐找到了特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地面...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團開始侵略山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和馬格亞那隊重逢的卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和沙漠鋼彈一起趕赴戰線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.28,0:23:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，追求和平也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.75,0:23:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了停止名為戰鬥的愚蠢行為
